{"tid":2060283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國共和黨: 草擬「警察改革法案」","createTime":"2020-06-11T14:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T19:29:59.000Z","uid":134071,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7eeb3fc4d134e0389495c3c1be5e7f7d7de6ec7f","tid":2060283,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"反警暴<br />\n已經成為兩黨共識<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/6/10/n12176132.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F6%2F10%2Fn12176132.htm&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0oc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=49cd1e8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/6/10/n12176132.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2020年06月11日訊】（大紀元英文記者Mimi Nguyen Ly報導／李言編譯）近日來，美國非裔男子弗洛伊德在警察執法期間死亡，引發各地的抗議活動。作為回應，美國國會兩黨均在積極推動警察改革法案。<br />\n<br />\n參議院多數黨領袖米奇&middot;麥康奈爾（Mitch McConnell）指定參議院中唯一的非裔共和黨參議員蒂姆&middot;斯科特（Tim Scott）來主導共和黨版本。<br />\n<br />\n麥康奈爾週二（9日）說，他請參議員蒂姆&middot;斯科特領導一個小組，該小組正在研究一項提案，以使參議院能夠應對「種族歧視」問題。"},{"pid":"112b96909e5c2529ed7a3411f2f48d2d31935fed","tid":2060283,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"華爾街日報的報導<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%A8%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B7%E8%8D%89%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E6%8F%90%E6%A1%88-11591756506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%258D%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25A1%2588-11591756506&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0oc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=abc8fb76\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%A8%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B7%E8%8D%89%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E6%8F%90%E6%A1%88-1159175